703900f-a.title: Brooklyn: Cropsey Avenue - 24th Avenue
703900f-a.text:
2409-2423 Cropsey Ave., east side, between Twenty Fourth Ave., and
Bay 37th Street. The frame house at right, No. 2423 Cropsey Ave., at the
corner of Bay 37th Street, is sunken because of the recent raising of all
street s in that neighborhood. Some homes are eight and ten feet below the
street level.
April 27, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
